Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:10.13,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,How is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:14.00,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I think his had more pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:17.14,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Darn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:19.97,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,No, I'll keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.47,0:00:32.47,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:48.05,Main - Italics,Nanami,0,0,0,,I don't want to make her cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:52.38,Main - Italics,Nanami,0,0,0,,I'm going to make sure she's always smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:33.52,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Dad's cooking...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:37.28,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,This is how Dad's tasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:43.24,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:45.46,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Thanks, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:49.22,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Nah, this is only something\Nwe could've pulled off together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:54.92,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Okay, maybe I'll try some \Nof your dad's fried fan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:02.58,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Nanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:06.04,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,It's nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:08.85,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,How strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:12.14,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,I've had this somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:17.20,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:21.62,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:24.77,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,You have me, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:29.92,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:32.92,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:34.40,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Fried fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:36.59,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Fried fan, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:38.30,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Shiroha-chan made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:39.28,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.71,0:03:44.47,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,A-Actually, I made it with Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.87,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Oh? You did, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:49.10,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Fried fan, hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:58.48,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,This flavor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:00.48,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:06.18,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Shiroha, I told you not to go near the diner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.67,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:12.81,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,We just wanted to recreate the chao—\Nthe fried fan that her father used to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:14.22,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Foolishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:17.35,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I... I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:21.09,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:22.37,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Shiroha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:27.09,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Why would you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:31.41,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Shiroha-chan worked so hard \Non that so you could have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:32.32,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:34.95,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Because you seemed sad too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:38.92,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,How could you be so awful?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:46.57,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,All this'll ever do is keep her \Ncaptive to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:48.89,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,That's not a good enough reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:51.76,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,You're hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:56.77,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Where is Shiroha-chan's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:05:01.09,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Shiroha-chan said she went somewhere far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:07.57,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Shiroha-chan was so happy when\N she was at the diner and cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:10.48,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Yet you told me to stay away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:14.71,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:20.11,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Isn't it a place full of good memories\Nof time well spent with her parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:27.54,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Not all memories are nice and pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:31.08,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,My wife once told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:34.76,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,"Our lineage has a strange power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:37.56,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,And that power comes at a price."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:41.15,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Power? At a price?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:45.96,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,"So we should strive not \Nto depend on our power."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:49.46,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,I'd ask her what that meant,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:51.47,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,but she'd only laugh and say...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.29,0:05:54.97,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,"We should just enjoy the summer."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:02.08,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,My daughter said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:06.24,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,That she wanted me to make sure \NShiroha could enjoy her summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:10.61,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,And then she vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:18.80,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Shiroha lost her gentle parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.75,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,What can a stubborn old \Nasshole like me do for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:26.76,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,But I {\i1}have{\i0} kept her away from the diner
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.82,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,so she wouldn't be fixated on her parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:33.76,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,I know I've treated her awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:35.42,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:38.48,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,And I appreciate what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:41.98,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,She's seemed so happy since you arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:47.99,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Her father was my son-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.99,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,He was sickly, but he was a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:56.37,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,And my daughter cared for that \Nrestless little girl with all her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:06:59.87,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,It's strange, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:03.10,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Why am I the only one left?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:05.32,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,An old geezer like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:20.77,Main - Italics,Nanami,0,0,0,,This summer is too full of sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:25.11,Main - Italics,Nanami,0,0,0,,I don't want anyone to be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:28.78,Main - Italics,Nanami,0,0,0,,Not Kobato-san or Shiroha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:31.59,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,I have to end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:33.46,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,That's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:37.53,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,I get the sense that I have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:41.37,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,But why do I feel this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.55,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:59.29,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,I know what I'm about to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:01.93,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,I... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:05.48,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,These...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:09.86,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,These are my memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:14.70,Flashback,Umi,0,0,0,,I want to throw paper \Nairplanes without fighting. {e18 21m30s}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:16.20,Flashback,Hairi;Shiroha,0,0,0,,Ready and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:18.66,Flashback,Hairi;Shiroha,0,0,0,,Takeoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:23.29,Flashback,Hairi,0,0,0,,Get this, Umi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:26.15,Flashback,Hairi,0,0,0,,Shiroha says she'll be your mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.96,Flashback,Shiroha,0,0,0,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:29.34,Flashback,Umi,0,0,0,,Oop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.44,Flashback,Hairi,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:37.22,Flashback,Hairi,0,0,0,,Say cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.68,Flashback,Dialogue,0,0,0,,It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:45.56,Flashback,Dialogue,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I got to see the fireworks.\N We kept our promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:49.57,Flashback,Umi,0,0,0,,I came to see Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:53.05,Flashback,Umi,0,0,0,,Because Mom's gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:55.55,Flashback,Umi,0,0,0,,Because I never knew her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:57.95,Flashback,Umi,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:01.66,Flashback,Hairi,0,0,0,,So you came to this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:05.14,Flashback,Hairi,0,0,0,,From the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:06.55,Flashback,Umi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:12.34,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:16.57,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,I came here from really far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:19.40,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,To this summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:25.39,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,To help the people dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:39.07,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:41.37,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,You're worried about me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:45.87,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,But I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:55.76,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,I'd already made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:15.78,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:17.31,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:41.18,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:45.47,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Why did you leave me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:48.57,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:50.10,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.07,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,A butterfly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:37.36,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,That dream again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:42.74,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,What was it saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:54.00,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,The parents are volunteering\Nat Shiroha-chan's school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:55.27,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.59,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:57.76,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:00.34,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:04.96,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,But wait... It's summer break right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:08.83,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,We need lanterns for the \NNatsudori ritual next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:11.02,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,There's a class for making them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:15.06,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,The parents usually take part.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:16.85,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:21.75,Main - Italics,Nanami,0,0,0,,This might be a good opportunity \Nfor the two of them to make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:24.77,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,I want you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:26.49,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:30.66,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Th-That won't do! You have to go, Kobato-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:34.54,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,I'm sure Shiroha-chan wants you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:37.33,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Even though she's been shut \Nin her room all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:42.13,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:48.76,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,I-I mean, you're really trying, \Ncooking and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:57.45,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Either way, the other kids \Nwill be scared if I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.82,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,I missed my chance to say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:11.33,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,The Natsudori festival, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:14.56,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,I remember making lanterns together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:18.12,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,That was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:21.80,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,The Natsudori dance was lovely too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:25.38,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:30.51,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,I just have to let Shiroha-chan \Nin on that memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:35.11,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,I'll make this a fun summer break,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:38.27,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,just like the one the three of us had together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:46.37,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,Well, I'm off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:47.94,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,Watch the house for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.01,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.24,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:52.08,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:56.32,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:58.32,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,She can never sit still.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:06.72,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs8\bord0\shad0\fay-.1\c&H857D6C&\b1\move(580.572,177.428,366.572,177.428)}Lanterns
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.04,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,Shiroha-chan's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:13.01,Default,Ao,0,0,0,,We're about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:14.27,Default,Miki,0,0,0,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:20.65,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,Her grandpa's not with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:22.64,Default,Ryoichi,0,0,0,,Shiroha-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:27.59,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Wow, I didn't expect there to be\N so many kids on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:33.18,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Shiroha-chan, we're gonna make \Nthe prettiest lanterns ever today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:33.98,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:39.92,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone, I'm going to tell you \Nabout the lanterns we're making today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:42.29,Default,All,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:46.30,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,These lanterns house \Nthe souls of the deceased.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:49.68,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Your grandparents, your pet cats...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.47,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Shiroha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:55.10,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,They contain the souls of all kinds of folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:59.60,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,And this special time of year is when\Nthey get to come back for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:02.94,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,They'll come to check in on all of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:05.11,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,then go back on the day of the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:08.59,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,So, to make sure they don't \Nget lost in the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:12.80,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,we light these lanterns \Nand send them on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:17.22,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,All right, everyone,\N let's make some lanterns!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.04,Default,All,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:21.12,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Shiroha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:23.03,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:25.38,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I don't want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:30.44,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,It's goodbye once we make them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:32.47,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,They're leaving, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:34.75,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Both Mom and Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:37.09,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:40.64,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Then I don't want to make this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:52.50,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Shiroha-chan, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:15:59.48,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Shiroha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:05.31,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:07.29,Default,Ai,0,0,0,,What did you do to Shiroha-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:09.32,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:12.90,Default,Miki,0,0,0,,I saw you say something to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:14.47,Default,Ao,0,0,0,,You said something awful, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:18.81,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,I-It's a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:20.22,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Sorry, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:21.56,Default,Ryoichi,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:23.03,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:25.44,Default,Ryoichi,0,0,0,,Don't bully Shiroha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:29.32,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ow, you're hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:51.41,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:53.79,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:57.71,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.13,0:16:59.60,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.09,0:17:01.76,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I miss you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:03.67,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I miss you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.62,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.83,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:30.88,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,We have a guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:40.48,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,I finally get to pay my respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:43.85,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,Sorry for dropping in like this, Kobato-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.39,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:47.20,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,I'm sure they're ecstatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:51.37,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,It was always Grandma Kato this, \NGrandma Kato that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:53.02,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,They were so attached to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:55.86,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,I appreciate you saying so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.94,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:18:00.37,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,I can't believe we lost Hitomi-chan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:06.37,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,Must be that Naruse power.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.68,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,Oh, jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:15.84,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,Being so old's made me such a worrywart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:19.34,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Hardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:23.35,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,Well, I'll get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:26.72,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,My old man is waiting at the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:29.35,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,You're more than welcome \Nto come together next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:31.51,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,I'll take you up on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.31,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,Say hi to Shiroha-chan for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:46.93,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:50.24,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Grandma Kato...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:53.12,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,Why, if it isn't Shiroha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:57.26,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,My, you've grown so tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:02.15,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,What a delight to run into you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:04.91,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,Maybe Hitomi-chan brought us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:08.02,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:11.02,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Do you know about my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:14.15,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Where did my mom go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:17.36,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Where did she go after she abandoned me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:25.92,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,Shiroha-chan, you mustn't say such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:35.29,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,You've gotten so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.93,0:19:40.82,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,I still remember the day you were\N born like it was yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.49,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:43.29,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:49.52,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,Hitomi-chan cared so much for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:53.67,Flashback,Hitomi,0,0,0,,Shiroha and I have the same power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:56.91,Flashback,Hitomi,0,0,0,,But in order to overcome it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:20:02.20,Flashback,Hitomi,0,0,0,,I want to make sure she \Nhas lots of fun summers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:07.95,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,She always thought about you above all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:15.23,Default,Grandma Kato,0,0,0,,So please, believe in Hitomi-chan... \Nin your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:25.93,Flashback - Italics,Hitomi,0,0,0,,Shiroha and I have the same power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:27.85,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,What did she mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:31.93,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,The same power as Mom...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:33.05,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,A power?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.05,0:20:36.26,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Strength? Influence?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:38.37,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,That doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:42.61,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, the first \Ntime I had that dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:52.25,Flashback,Hitomi,0,0,0,,Did I wake you? Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:55.94,Flashback,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Mom, I had a weird dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:58.14,Flashback,Hitomi,0,0,0,,What was it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:00.56,Flashback,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:10.22,Flashback,Shiroha,0,0,0,,A strange butterfly told me that \NI have the power to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.18,0:21:14.69,Flashback,Shiroha,0,0,0,,See? Isn't that weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:18.17,Flashback,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:19.55,Flashback,Hitomi,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:21.21,Flashback,Hitomi,0,0,0,,It was just a weird dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:25.53,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Soon after that, Mom vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:29.53,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,If she and I have the same power,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:35.11,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,she might have gone to see Dad first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:36.64,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:38.64,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Shiroha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:42.59,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:44.83,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:47.63,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Thank goodness. I was so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:50.79,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Everyone else is worried about you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:56.60,Default,Nanami,0,0,0,,Shiroha-chan, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.60,0:21:57.32,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:21:59.10,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
